                            <comment id="15714960" author="srowen" created="Fri, 2 Dec 2016 12:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s helpful if you point out specifically what you mean in the code, but I think it&apos;s this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; l = i.toLong
      val rand = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; XORShiftRandom(seed)
      &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (input.hasNext) {
        val item = input.next()
        val replacementIndex = (rand.nextDouble() * l).toLong
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (replacementIndex &amp;lt; k) {
          reservoir(replacementIndex.toInt) = item
        }
        l += 1
      }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;l needs to be incremented before the random choice, right?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
